42:42.302 --> 42:43.542
Okay.

42:43.562 --> 42:47.063
You're probably gonna have
questions about this,

42:47.290 --> 42:49.640
maybe tonight
or maybe in the future,

42:49.793 --> 42:53.218
but I promise you I'll answer
any question you have forever.

42:53.238 --> 42:54.312
Okay?

